  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want DApps to remember my preferences so that I can skip unnecessary screens on later runs. \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Bancor offers to remember the user's preference between the Bancor wallet and \"localhost\" (Status), but the preference is not saved when selecting local host.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\"Remember my selection\" saves my preference for the Status wallet and I am not asked again on later use.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe wallet selection screen appears no matter what.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/40891467-5d8cdfb8-6786-11e8-8b9f-844db5bf2dce.png\" width=250/>\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Bancor\r\n- Select wallet \"local host\"\r\n- Check \"Remember my selection\"\r\n- Make transaction\r\n- Close Bancor\r\n- Reopen Bancor\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.19\r\n* Operating System: Android OnePlus ONEPLUS A5010 \r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nhttps://insta.co/bugs/BthG382psRi6IKjY4h-pxg\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"/favicon.ico?v=eE5LjeB9Od\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><strong><a href=\"https://insta.co/bugs/BthG382psRi6IKjY4h-pxg\">Bug #BthG382psRi6IKjY4h-pxg | Instabug</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
